text: Nadine Jenny (born 13 June 1990) is a Swiss volleyball player. She played at the 2013 Montreux Volley Masters and 2013 CEV Volleyball European Championship. She played for Voléro Zürich and Sm'Aesch Pfeffingen. == References == Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss volleyball players
